{"id":106506,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/简讯：日官员吁避免极端民族主义/","date":"2010-09-21T23:06:15Z","modified":"2010-09-21T23:06:15Z","title":"简讯：日官员吁避免极端民族主义","content":"<div>\n<p>日本官方长官仙谷由人星期二（9月21日）就中日间日益升级的争吵发表评论。</p>\n<p>他呼吁双方避免刺激“狭隘的极端民族主义”。</p>\n<p>他还表示中日间的友好关系对区域发展有着重要意义。</p>\n<p>日本国土交通相马渊澄夫同日宣布将拒绝会晤到日本参加亚太经合组织旅游部长会议的中国国家旅游局副局长。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ejeB-2JnLo2lhOK1q3mJKu4ZJVY/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ejeB-2JnLo2lhOK1q3mJKu4ZJVY/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ejeB-2JnLo2lhOK1q3mJKu4ZJVY/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ejeB-2JnLo2lhOK1q3mJKu4ZJVY/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ZAs7iVmXCGc:1mcUP3xFtT4:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ZAs7iVmXCGc:1mcUP3xFtT4:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ZAs7iVmXCGc:1mcUP3xFtT4:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ZAs7iVmXCGc:1mcUP3xFtT4:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ZAs7iVmXCGc:1mcUP3xFtT4:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=ZAs7iVmXCGc:1mcUP3xFtT4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/ZAs7iVmXCGc\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhong